00:03:44.065 --> 00:03:53.440
Whenever the enemy says he is going to destroy, we say, 'Oh, no, you're not.

00:03:56.930 --> 00:03:58.712
We have power and authority over you.

00:03:58.712 --> 00:04:07.269
' Not our churches, not our houses, not our places of worship.

00:04:07.269 --> 00:04:09.260
