Gilmore said 9,000 people were born again in Cuba and 42,000 came to the meeting.

00:19:19.900 --> 00:19:33.109
97 pastors came to get refired up and spread the gospel through the nations.

00:19:33.109 --> 00:19:42.000
Father, we thank You for the platform of YouTube, X, and even Facebook.

