00:21:46.602 --> 00:22:08.760
When I hear my friend Billy Burke talk about how he had stage four cancer and he couldn't even see out of one eye because he had double vision—he was on the verge of death.

00:22:21.735 --> 00:22:22.000
The doctors said, "You're going to die in just a couple of days.

00:22:22.000 --> 00:22:31.910
" He was 11 or 12 years old, I believe, on the verge of death.

00:22:31.910 --> 00:22:45.240
