00:24:05.371 --> 00:24:12.215
I hear that testimony all the time, and I think about it.

00:24:12.215 --> 00:24:17.857
That's the same thing that has happened to my Megan.

00:24:17.857 --> 00:24:20.360
Do you believe?

00:24:20.360 --> 00:24:23.000
Do you believe?

00:24:23.000 --> 00:24:29.093
