00:26:24.464 --> 00:26:40.075
I believe that it's your day, your expiration date for sickness, as we see throughout this day that Jesus took it all on the cross.

00:26:40.075 --> 00:26:46.400
He was whipped to the point of being unrecognizable.

00:26:46.400 --> 00:26:53.080
