00:26:53.080 --> 00:27:01.400
He suffered greatly for you to walk in victory over sickness.

00:27:01.400 --> 00:27:06.954
By His stripes, we are healed.

00:27:06.954 --> 00:27:10.345
That's why we take this.

00:27:12.435 --> 00:27:22.400
This isn't a religious act; this is in remembrance of what He did for us.

00:27:22.400 --> 00:27:26.520
Jesus took it all for you.

00:27:26.520 --> 00:27:35.540
I'm not going to allow the devil to put on me what Jesus took.

00:27:35.540 --> 00:27:39.635
I'm not taking his 'poo poo package.

00:27:39.635 --> 00:27:51.030
' He takes the FedEx 'poo poo package' and he puts it at your door to see if you accept it.

00:27:54.650 --> 00:27:56.120
I say, "I'm not accepting it.

00:28:03.470 --> 00:28:03.685
I am not allowing autism to stay on my child anymore.

00:28:17.800 --> 00:28:18.185
I am not allowing my life to keep being this way.

00:28:18.185 --> 00:28:18.955
" Why?

00:28:18.955 --> 00:28:25.526
Because Jesus paid the price for you to walk in victory over it.

00:28:25.526 --> 00:28:33.789
It wasn't just for salvation; Jesus paid the price for you to be healed.

00:28:52.890 --> 00:28:53.265
Jesus paid the price for you to be prosperous.

00:29:02.000 --> 00:29:02.245
