00:29:02.245 --> 00:29:05.533
You don't have to be poor anymore.

00:29:05.533 --> 00:29:16.111
You don't have to be broke, busted, and disgusted, down and out, thinking, "How am I going to get through this life anymore?

00:29:16.111 --> 00:29:20.526
