00:30:02.990 --> 00:30:09.613
My peace I leave with you; my peace I give unto you.

00:30:17.613 --> 00:30:17.782
I receive peace, joy, and His patience tonight.

00:30:17.782 --> 00:30:18.900
Thank You, Lord.

00:30:18.900 --> 00:30:20.747
By faith, I receive more.

00:30:31.155 --> 00:30:32.153
