00:30:45.720 --> 00:30:53.240
My Father gives it to me.

00:30:57.000 --> 00:30:57.180
I yield to self-control, joy, and longsuffering.

00:31:05.865 --> 00:31:06.090
I yield, Father, to everything the fruits of the Spirit say I can have.

00:31:06.090 --> 00:31:18.909
Father, tonight we take this body right now in Jesus' name, and we give You glory, honor, and praise for what You did 2,000-plus years ago.

00:31:18.909 --> 00:31:25.484
Lord Jesus, You became the ultimate sacrifice for us.

00:31:33.920 --> 00:31:34.467
